This app let's you to make behavior packs for Minecraft Bedrock Edition with your structures. It only requires your MCSTRUCTURE file and it generates the behavior pack as a MCPACK file.
This app is not affiliated with Mojang Studios or Xbox Game Studios or Minecraft or Minecraft Bedrock Edition. This is just a fanmade open-source app made with TurboWarp (mod of Scratch).
